2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as pose estimation is a crucial task in robotics and the paper discusses how to remove ambiguity in the estimation. 
3. cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with geometric configurations and their detection. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper may involve the use of machine learning techniques for circle detection and pose estimation. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper may involve the use of AI techniques for circle detection and pose estimation.
